{"tid":2076180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷念建制派愛國愛港劉馬車","createTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T12:40:26.000Z","uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73b7cb5d17e859072091e8a18bd8ebdc4d60e8e6","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LCQddua980I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLCQddua980I&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=2f021098\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LCQddua980I</a>"},{"pid":"bf5f166365ac28740a0c14157f50884bbad0c272","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h667wYPfC60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh667wYPfC60&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b65c8a7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h667wYPfC60</a>"},{"pid":"acc469eeaaa49d71ec8464746afc698078489769","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>馬車送給全香港警察:《Forever Love》永遠愛您們</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TFjpSGBMhTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTFjpSGBMhTc&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=92a0576a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TFjpSGBMhTc</a>"},{"pid":"7cd7f9d660b9d7192ee4351ab99afcdea5f95f56","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劉馬車出席警察同盟會！</span><br />\n文/積遜猿<br />\n<br />\n香港「警察同盟會」喺6月13日舉辦晚宴，咁多退休嘅警察朋友聚首同堂，緊係要支持返警察最近爭議好多，俾網民狂插嘅執法行動喇！咁其實本身都好正常，直頭係合情、合理、合法；和平、理性、非暴力嘅典範。<br />\n<br />\n片段可見，警察話完香港示威者之後，隨即介紹劉馬車登場，講佢最近俾「暴徒」毒打。劉馬車攞咗枝咪就開始批評示威者，「呢班廢青搞搞震」，「香港好地地，係都要搞亂香港先得」，千錯萬錯都係示威者嘅錯。<br />\n<br />\n劉馬車講自己俾人襲擊，講到眉飛色舞，在座嘅各位警察朋友都拍哂手掌，相當認同劉馬車嘅言論。Well，有網民話佢哋俾「更生人士」一個機會，都係好事嚟嘅。<br />\n<br />\n「youtube 片已被有關人仕刪除，未知有無backup」"},{"pid":"530f33bc7440311059241c79a3cfcaeb7fc183fe","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">譚詠麟、梁家輝大讚馬車:香港年青人嘅榜樣！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKcoTA7rv8M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLKcoTA7rv8M&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=5692fb5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKcoTA7rv8M</a>"},{"pid":"486e28596103e4bb5b3970d101a344c09d672eb7","tid":2076180,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"愛國梅毒青年"},{"pid":"7f5c4b4f2d9435b830600a6f14cda35847cc3494","tid":2076180,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立法會議員梁美芬大讚馬車:如果馬車係我個仔，我短幾年命都制！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vaPG-EWEqAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvaPG-EWEqAo&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=36584982\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vaPG-EWEqAo</a>"},{"pid":"d08c6b5f156d2a5ff8993172234cc970fb28f04d","tid":2076180,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TGXzMxu9WVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTGXzMxu9WVw&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=2b75468a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TGXzMxu9WVw</a>"},{"pid":"8a3a564bb64b730ffb7a9d8d9635232407ab1ef0","tid":2076180,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"馬車菜刀桶屎眼<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.thisav.com/video/44115/%